  {
   "start": 459.24,
   "end": 461.24,
   "text": "So matter grows in space"
  },
  {
   "start": 461.24,
   "end": 462.24,
   "text": "But the time that matter takes"
  },
  {
   "start": 462.24,
   "end": 464.24,
   "text": "To grow in space is infinite"
  },
  {
   "start": 464.24,
   "end": 465.24,
   "text": "So"
  },
  {
   "start": 465.24,
   "end": 466.24,
   "text": "Um"
  },
  {
   "start": 466.24,
   "end": 467.24,
   "text": "Now"
  },
  {
   "start": 467.24,
   "end": 468.24,
   "text": "I"
  },
  {
   "start": 468.24,
   "end": 470.24,
   "text": "The reason I believe in reincarnation"
  },
  {
   "start": 470.24,
   "end": 471.24,
   "text": "Is because"
  },
  {
   "start": 471.24,
   "end": 473.24,
   "text": "Well it makes more sense to me"
  },
  {
   "start": 473.24,
   "end": 474.24,
   "text": "But it also"
  },
  {
   "start": 474.24,
