  {
   "start": 536.81,
   "end": 537.81,
   "text": "In all of your lives"
  },
  {
   "start": 537.81,
   "end": 538.81,
   "text": "You get to experience everything"
  },
  {
   "start": 538.81,
   "end": 539.81,
   "text": "So that you can have"
  },
  {
