  {
   "start": 543.81,
   "end": 544.81,
   "text": "You know"
  },
  {
   "start": 544.81,
   "end": 545.81,
   "text": "You're the wisest"
  },
  {
   "start": 545.81,
   "end": 546.81,
   "text": "Once you become a demigod"
  },
  {
   "start": 546.81,
   "end": 547.81,
   "text": "Or that"
  },
  {
   "start": 547.81,
   "end": 548.81,
   "text": "So you can become a demigod"
  },
  {
   "start": 548.81,
   "end": 549.81,
   "text": "Or a god"
  },
  {
   "start": 549.81,
   "end": 550.81,
   "text": "Um"
  },
  {
   "start": 550.81,
   "end": 552.81,
   "text": "So"
  },
  {
   "start": 552.81,
   "end": 554.81,
   "text": "That seems unfair"
  },
  {
   "start": 554.81,
   "end": 555.81,
   "text": "And how about animals"
